data.title: Crazy Ethereum Liquidity Crunch Spotted on OKX
data.description: OKX exchange has released its latest proof-of-reserve (PoR) report that shows a dip in users’ Ethereum holdings. According to the report, assets like Bitcoin and Tether BINANCE:USDTUSD saw a significant jump, while Ethereum declined month-on-month.Ethereum liquidity crunch incoming?OKX released the…
